Uralkali Gains Most in a Month on Belaruskali Valuation

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-08-10T15:36:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-10/uralkali-advances-most-in-five-months-on-belaruskali-valuation.html
OAO Uralkali,  Russia ’s biggest
potash producer, jumped the most in almost a month after New
Delhi-based Mint said  India  may buy 20 percent to 25 percent of
Belaruskali in Belarus for $7 billion.  Uralkali shares gained 2.2 percent to 248.03 rubles by the
6:45 p.m. close in Moscow, their biggest gain since July 13.  “It is a high valuation,” Marco Casas, vice-president of
equity sales at Otkritie Capital, said in e-mailed comments.
“Uralkali is being supported by the news,”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
